{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"Grade","mdn_url":"/pt-BR/docs/Glossary/Grid","locale":"pt-BR","native":"Português (do Brasil)","sidebarHTML":"\n<ol>\n <li>CSS Grid Layout Guide:<br>\n  <em><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/CSS_Grid_Layout/Basic_Concepts_of_Grid_Layout\">Basic concepts of grid layout</a></em></li>\n <li>Property reference\n  <ol>\n   <li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/CSS/grid-template-columns\"><code>grid-template-columns</code></a></li>\n   <li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/CSS/grid-template-rows\"><code>grid-template-rows</code></a></li>\n   <li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/CSS/grid\"><code>grid</code></a></li>\n   <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/grid-template\"><code>grid-template</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n  </ol>\n </li>\n</ol>\n","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p>Uma&nbsp;<em>grade no CSS&nbsp;</em>é definida usando o&nbsp;valor <code>grid</code>&nbsp;da propriedade&nbsp;<a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/CSS/display\"><code>display</code></a>; você pode definir colunas e linhas na sua grade usando as propridades&nbsp;<a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/CSS/grid-template-rows\"><code>grid-template-rows</code></a> e <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/CSS/grid-template-columns\"><code>grid-template-columns</code></a>.</p>\n\n<p>A grade que você define usando essas propriedades é descrita como uma <em>grade explícita</em>.</p>\n\n<p>Se você colocar o conteúdo fora dessa grade explícita ou se estiver utilizando o posicionamento automático e o algoritmo da grade precisar criar linhas ou colunas adicionais <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Glossary/Grid_Tracks\">tracks <small>(en-US)</small></a> para manter <a class=\"page-not-created\" title=\"A documentação sobre isto ainda não foi escrita; por favor considere contribuir!\">grid items</a>, então serão criadas faixas extras na grade implícita. A <em>grade implícita</em> é a grade criada automaticamente devido ao conteúdo adicionado fora das faixas definidas.</p>\n\n<p>No exemplo abaixo, criamos uma <em>grade explícita</em> de três colunas e duas linhas. A terceira linha da grade é uma <em>faixa implícita de linha da grade</em>, formada por serem mais do que os seis os itens que preenchem as faixas explícitas.</p>\n\n<div id=\"example\">\n\n\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: css notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token selector\">.wrapper</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">display</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> grid<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">grid-template-columns</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 1fr 1fr 1fr<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">grid-template-rows</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 100px 100px<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: html notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>div</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">class</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>wrapper<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span> Um <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span> dois <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span> três <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span> quatro <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span> cinco <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span> seis <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span> sete <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span> oito <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n</code></pre></div>\n</div>\n\n<p><iframe class=\"sample-code-frame\" title=\"example sample\" id=\"frame_example\" width=\"500\" height=\"330\" src=\"https://yari-demos.prod.mdn.mozit.cloud/pt-BR/docs/Glossary/Grid/_sample_.example.html\" loading=\"lazy\"></iframe></p>"}}],"toc":[],"summary":"Uma grade no CSS é definida usando o valor grid da propriedade display; você pode definir colunas e linhas na sua grade usando as propridades grid-template-rows e grid-template-columns.","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"Grid","locale":"de","native":"Deutsch"},{"title":"Grid","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"Grid","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"Grille","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"Grid (グリッド)","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"Grid","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"},{"title":"Grid","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"},{"title":"Grid","locale":"zh-TW","native":"正體中文 (繁體)"}],"source":{"folder":"pt-br/glossary/grid","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/pt-br/glossary/grid/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/pt-BR/docs/Glossary","title":"Glossário"},{"uri":"/pt-BR/docs/Glossary/Grid","title":"Grade"}],"pageTitle":"Grade - Glossário | MDN","noIndexing":false}}